      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "UNITED STATES DEPARTMENT OF JUSTICE",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "FEDERAL BUREAU OF INVESTIGATION",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "Dallas, Texas",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "October 10, 1967",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "In Reply, Please Refer to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "File No.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "Re: UNIDENTIFIED FLYING OBJECTS;",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "ANONYMOUS INFORMANT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "DALLAS, TEXAS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "OCTOBER 9, 1967",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "A young white female, who refused to give her name,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "appeared at the Dallas FBI Office on October 9, 1967. She",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "stated she is interested in Unidentified Flying Objects (UFOs)",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "and has received a quantity of information concerning beings",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "from outer space. She stated she will not reveal her identity",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "as she would feel like a fool if this information is not true.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "She stated if it is true, however, she will meet with interested",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "officials and furnish all the information she has, provided",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "nothing is done to endanger her safety.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "She stated in July, 1967, she met a being from another",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "planet who had assumed earthly form. He gave her certain",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "information, then he was picked up and departed from the earth",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "on August 21, 1967. She stated she then received messages from",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "non-earthly sources in a manner she refused to discuss. She",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "stated these sources told her of the following:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "(1) An antimissile missile was fired at a UFO",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "over Africa on May 22, 1962, but the UFO",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "was protected by its \"force field.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "(2) A UFO was detected 22,000 miles from earth by",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "radar about August 6, 1967.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "(3) A UFO was detected over Antarctica August 20,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "1967.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "(4) A UFO was detected over the \"Dewline\" in the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "past week and was shot down, and beings from",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "outer space are trying to recover it.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "Informant would furnish no further details. She stated",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "if this information is true, she will know other information",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "This document contains neither recommendations",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "nor conclusions of the FBI. It is the property",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "of the FBI and is loaned to your agency; it and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "its contents are not to be distributed outside",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "your agency.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "text": "ENCLOSURE",
      "status": "image_matched"
    }
